OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FFree bets and moneyback guarantee
OL,8,Foffers lure more people to place a bet
OL,9,Fand spend more money, particularly
OL,10,Fthose at risk of problem gambling, a
OL,11,Fstudy has found.
OL,13,FThe ESRI's Behavioural Research Unit
OL,14,Falso found that people were three
OL,15,Ftimes more likely to spend money on
OL,16,Fbad bets after being shown an offer.
