OL,3,CFree bets coax people into betting
OL,4,Cmore, including problem gamblers `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe new research, funded by the
OL,8,FGambling Regulatory Authority of
OL,9,FIreland (GRAI), used a controlled
OL,10,Fexperiment to test whether offers, or
OL,11,F"inducements", alter betting behaviour.
OL,13,FThe experiment was run with a sample
OL,14,Fof 622 men under 40 just prior to the
OL,15,FEuro 2024 football championship.
OL,17,FParticipants were given money to place
OL,18,Fup to six realistic bets on Euro 2024
OL,19,Fmatches.
