OL,3,CFree bets coax people into betting
OL,4,Cmore, including problem gamblers `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FParticipants exposed to the offers
OL,8,Fwere three times more likely to spend
OL,9,Fmoney on these bad bets.
OL,11,FThe study also found that those at
OL,12,Frisk of problem gambling were more
OL,13,Faffected by the inducements than those
OL,14,Fnot at risk.
OL,16,FAfter the experiment, participants
OL,17,Fanswered questions about their
OL,18,Funderstanding of the inducements.
