OL,3,CFree bets coax people into betting
OL,4,Cmore, including problem gamblers `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FEven though most of the participants
OL,8,Fwere regular bettors, most did not
OL,9,Frealise that there were restrictions
OL,10,Fon free bets, and many did not know
OL,11,Fthat they would not receive their
OL,12,Fstake back if they won a free bet,
OL,13,Fboth of which are standard practice in
OL,14,Fthe market.
OL,16,FDr Diarmaid O Ceallaigh, of the ESRI's
OL,17,FBehavioural Research Unit, said that
OL,18,Fthe findings call for stricter
OL,19,Fregulation of gambling offers in
OL,20,FIreland.
