OL,3,CFree bets coax people into betting
OL,4,Cmore, including problem gamblers `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FHe said: "Our findings imply that
OL,8,Fgambling offers aren't merely
OL,9,Fmarketing tools, but pose a real risk
OL,10,Fof financial harm, particularly among
OL,11,Fvulnerable groups.
OL,13,F"The results support the case for
OL,14,Fstricter regulation of gambling offers
OL,15,Fin Ireland, following steps already
OL,16,Ftaken in other European countries,
OL,17,Fsuch as banning sign-up bonuses,
OL,18,Frestricting offers to at-risk
OL,19,Findividuals, and capping their value."
