OL,7,FChief executive of Gambling Regulatory
OL,8,FAuthority of Ireland Anne Marie
OL,9,FCaulfield said she welcomed the the
OL,10,Ffindings and said they "add weight to
OL,11,Fthe discourse" around the harms of
OL,12,Fgambling inducements.
OL,14,FShe said: "We are committed to
OL,15,Fcontinued research to understand the
OL,16,Fextent of gambling in Ireland, the
OL,17,Fdrivers of gambling harms and the
OL,18,Fimpact of inducements and advertising
OL,19,Fon gambling behaviours.
