OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,F"We are actively engaged with a broad
OL,8,Frange of stakeholders including with
OL,9,Findustry, charities and with people
OL,10,Fwho have lived experience of harm
OL,11,Fcaused by gambling.
OL,13,F"The Gambling Regulation Act 2024 sets
OL,14,Fout obligations for licensees in the
OL,15,Fway in which inducements can be
OL,16,Foffered, including a ban on targeted
OL,17,Finducements, and the findings of this
OL,18,Fstudy affirm these measures."
